ay%20from%20the%20theatre%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20was%20the%20police%20who%20were%20clearing%20the%20way%20for%20him%20and%20he%20reached%20the%20venue%20under%20their%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20alleged%20that%20before%20entering%20the%20theatre%20and%20exiting%2C%20the%20actor%20stood%20through%20the%20sunroof%20of%20his%20car%20and%20waved%20to%20the%20crowds%20in%20a%20roadshow%2C%20leading%20to%20thousands%20of%20fans%20jostling%20to%20get%20a%20glimpse%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20said%20thousands%20of%20fans%20gathered%20when%20the%20actor%20reached%20as%20there%20are%20several%20theatres%20in%20the%20locality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor's%20private%20security%20pushed%20aside%20the%20fans%2C%20which%20led%20to%20a%20stampede-like%20situation%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%2C%20who%20narrated%20the%20incident%2C%20said%20the%20theatre%20management%20did%20not%20initially%20allow%20a%20police%20official%20to%20meet%20the%20actor%20to%20convey%20him%20to%20leave%20the%20place%20in%20view%20of%20the%20prevailing%20situation.%20However%2C%20the%20official%20reached%20the%20actor%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20leave%2C%20as%20the%20crowd%20would%20not%20go%20unless%20he%20left.%20The%20actor%20did%20not%20budge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20police%20official%2C%20who%20then%20reached%20the%20spot%2C%20told%20the%20actor%20to%20leave%20the%20place%20immediately%2C%20failing%20which%2C%20he%20would%20have%20to%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20police%20station%20as%20the%20situation%20was%20out%20of%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20senior%20official%20forced%20the%20actor%20out%20of%20the%20theatre.%20Even%20while%20leaving%2C%20the%20actor%20again%20waved%20to%20the%20crowd.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20type%20of%20person%20(the%20actor%20was)%26quot%3B%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actor%20allegedly%20did%20not%20behave%20properly%20with%20the%20police%20when%20the%20latter%20reached%20his%20residence%20to%20inform%20him%20about%20the%20case%20against%20him%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20slammed%20film%20personalities%20for%20making%20a%20beeline%20for%20Allu%20Arjun's%20residence%20to%20meet%20him%20after%20his%20arrest%20but%20not%20showing%20empathy%20to%20visit%20the%20boy%20who%20is%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20hospital%20and%20faced%20a%20brain%20dead-like%20situation%20after%20suffering%20injuries%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20appeal%20to%20the%20top%20film%20personalities%20that%20they%20should%20not%20be%20inhuman%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20(Allu%20Arjun)%20was%20taken%20to%20police%20station%20for%20a%20day%2C%20the%20high%20court%20also%20accepted%20lunch%20motion%20petition%20and%20gave%20him%20bail.%20Our%20people%20are%20saying%20release%20him%20at%2012%20in%20the%20night.%20Where%20is%20the%20provision%20(to%20release%20at%20midnight)%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20he%20is%20continuously%20monitoring%20the%20boy's%20health%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20industry%20can%20take%20incentives%2C%20and%20subsidies%20from%20the%20government%20but%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20special%20privileges%20when%20untoward%20incidents%20like%20death%20in%20a%20stampede%20happen%20and%20said%20the%20government%20would%20not%20spare%20those%20who%20troubled%20common%20people%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20attacked%20BRS%20working%20president%20K%20T%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20without%20naming%20him%2C%20for%20his%20criticism%20of%20the%20government%20when%20Allu%20Arjun%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Cinematography%20Minister%20Komatireddy%20Venkat%20Reddy%20spoke%20against%20allowing%20'benefit%20shows'%20in%20the%20night%20without%20permissions.%20He%20announced%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20assistance%20from%20his%20side%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20besides%20the%20government%20taking