s%20role%20as%20Rafael%20Solano%20during%20its%202014-2019%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20company's%C2%A0LinkedIn%C2%A0page%2C%20Baldoni%20co-founded%20the%20production%20studio%20Wayfarer%20Entertainment%20in%202013%2C%20which%20later%20produced%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20With%20Us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fit-ends-with-us-blake-lively-justin-baldoni-feud-rumors-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIt%20Ends%20With%20Us%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20production%2C%20based%20on%20the%20novel%20of%20the%20same%20name%20by%20Colleen%20Hoover%2C%20was%20plagued%20with%20rumors%20that%20Lively%20and%20Baldoni%20had%20developed%20a%20feud%20while%20on%20set.%20Business%20Insider%20reported%20that%20Baldoni%20had%20been%20largely%20absent%20from%20press%20events%20with%20other%20cast%20members%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20were%20not%20photographed%20together%20during%20the%20film's%20premiere.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELively%20faced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-backlash-it-ends-with-us-promotion-save-reputation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esignificant%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20amid%20the%20rumored%20feud%2C%20with%20fans%20turning%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BGossip%20Girl%26quot%3B%20star%20and%20suggesting%20she%20was%20unlikeable%20and%20difficult%20to%20work%20with%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20lawsuit%2C%20Lively%20accused%20Baldoni%20of%20sexual%20harassment%2C%20retaliation%2C%20and%20breach%20of%20contract%2C%20saying%20the%20actor%20inflicted%20%26quot%3Bemotional%20distress%26quot%3B%20and%20conspired%20to%20damage%20her%20public%20reputation%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20film's%20release.%20Baldoni's%20attorney%20has%20called%20the%20claims%20made%20in%20the%20complaint%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20false%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20salacious.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original