ard%20work%20and%20putting%20the%20team%20above%20everything%20else.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20you%20bid%20farewell%20to%20international%20cricket%2C%20jersey%20number%2099%20will%20be%20sorely%20missed.%20Cricket%20lovers%20will%20miss%20the%20sense%20of%20expectation%20they%20felt%20when%20you%20took%20to%20the%20crease%20to%20bowl%20-%20there%20was%20always%20a%20feeling%20that%20you%20were%20weaving%20a%20web%20around%20the%20opponents%20which%20would%20trap%20a%20victim%20any%20moment.%20You%20possessed%20an%20uncanny%20ability%20to%20outwit%20batsmen%20with%20good%20old%20off-spin%20as%20well%20as%20innovative%20variations%2C%20as%20the%20situation%20demanded.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEach%20one%20of%20the%20765%20international%20wickets%20that%20you%20took%20across%20all%20formats%20was%20special.%20Holding%20the%20record%20of%20having%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20Player%20of%20the%20Series%20awards%20in%20Test%20matches%20shows%20the%20impact%20you%20had%20on%20the%20team's%20success%20in%20Tests%20over%20the%20last%20many%20years.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20a%20young%20prospect%2C%20you%20took%20a%20five-wicket%20haul%20on%20Test%20debut%20and%20went%20on%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20winning%20squad%20in%202011.%20By%20the%20time%20you%20bowled%20the%20team%20to%20victory%20in%20the%20last%20over%20of%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%202013%2C%20you%20had%20become%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20team.%20Later%2C%20you%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20as%20a%20senior%20in%20the%20team%20through%20multiple%20victories%20in%20all%20formats%20of%20the%20game.%20As%20a%20player%20who%20has%20been%20the%20ICC%20Cricketer%20of%20the%20Year%2C%20you%20have%20also%20won%20international%20acclaim%20and%20universal%20respect.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYou%20have%20showcased%20your%20all-round%20prowess%20by%20scoring%20a%20century%20and%20taking%20five%20wickets%20in%20the%20same%20match%2C%20many%20times.%20With%20the%20bat%20in%20hand%2C%20too%2C%20you%20have%20given%20our%20nation%20many%20memories%20including%20the%20brave%20match-saving%20innings%20in%20Sydney%20in%202021.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOften%20people%20are%20remembered%20for%20some%20wonderful%20shot%20that%20they%20played.%20But%20you%20have%20the%20unique%20distinction%20of%20being%20remembered%20for%20both%20a%20shot%20and%20a%20leave%20in%20the%20legendary%20match%20of%20the%20WT20%20in%202022.%20Your%20winning%20shot%20elicited%20great%20cheers.%20The%20way%20you%20left%20the%20ball%20before%20it%2C%20allowing%20it%20on%20its%20way%20to%20becoming%20a%20wide%20ball%2C%20showed%20your%20presence%20of%20mind.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEven%20during%20moments%20of%20adversity%2C%20your%20sincerity%20and%20commitment%20came%20to%20the%20fore.%20We%20all%20remember%20the%20way%20you%20flew%20back%20to%20contribute%20to%20the%20team%20even%20when%20your%20mother%20was%20hospitalised%20and%20the%20time%20you%20kept%20playing%20against%20South%20Africa%20even%20when%20you%20couldn't%20get%20in%20touch%20with%20your%20family%20during%20the%20floods%20in%20Chennai.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAs%20one%20observes%20your%20career%2C%20your%20flexibility%20and%20adaptability%20stand%20out.%20The%20way%20you%20tailored%20your%20approach%20to%20suit%20various%20formats%20of%20the%20game%20was%20an%20asset%20to%20the%20team.%20I%20wonder%20if%20your%20education%20as%20an%20engineer%20helped%20you%20in%20the%20meticulous%20and%20detail-oriented%20approach%20that%20you%20are%20famous%20for.%20Many%20analysts%20and%20peers%20have%20praised%20your%20sharp%20cricketing%20brain.%20I%20am%20confident%20that%20such%20knowledge%20will%20come%20of%20use%20to%20youngsters%20of%20future%20generations.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20wit%20and%20warmth%20that%20you%20bring%20to%20your%20conversations%20have%20been%20appreciated%20by%20fans.%20I%20ho