India%20head%20coach%20Ravi%20Shastri%20believes%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20was%20justified%20in%20celebrating%20on%20avoiding%20the%20follow-on%20during%20the%20rain-hit%20third%20Test%20against%20Australia%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20five-match%20series%20being%20locked%20at%201-1.%20On%20Day%20Four%20of%20the%20match%20at%20the%20Gabba%2C%20Akash%20Deep%20sliced%20a%20Pat%20Cummins%20delivery%20over%20the%20gully%20for%20a%20boundary%2C%20which%20helped%20India%20avoid%20the%20follow-on%2C%20leading%20to%20jubilant%20celebrations%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20by%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%2C%20head%20coach%20Gautam%20Gambhir%20and%20Virat%20Kohli.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20many%20in%20the%20Australian%20camp%20were%20surprised%20by%20it%2C%20Shastri%20felt%20there%20was%20nothing%20bad%20about%20it.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20should%20celebrate.%20It%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20character%20from%20the%20last%20pair%20with%2035-36%20runs%20needed.%20That%20celebration%20showed%20they%20knew%20the%20importance%20of%20that%20effort%20within%20the%20dressing%20room%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20series.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20one%20thing%20following-on%2C%20it's%20one%20thing%20then%20again%20being%202-3%20down%20as%20opposed%20to%2C%20you%20going%20ahead%20and%20rattling%20the%20Australian%20top-order.%20It%20is%20fully%20justified%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Shastri%20on%20the%20ICC%20Review%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20scenes%20in%20Brisbane%2C%20Shastri%20recalled%20the%2089-run%20partnership%20between%20Bumrah%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami%20at%20the%20Lord's%20during%20the%202021%20series%20against%20England%2C%20a%20match%20which%20India%20eventually%20won.%20He%20also%20highlighted%20the%20importance%20of%20lower-order%20bailing%20India%20out%20of%20tough%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20reminded%20me%20of%20the%20celebration%2C%20in%20COVID%20times%20when%20Jasprit%20and%20Mohammed%20Shami