n%3Cp%3EAt%20first%2C%20as%20people%20laid%20flowers%20outside%20the%20church%20in%20the%20early%20morning%2C%20there%20were%20just%20expressions%20of%20sorrow%20and%20grief.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAndrea%20Reis%2C%2057%2C%20arrived%20with%20her%20daughter%20Julia%2C%2034%2C%20and%20reflected%20on%20a%20narrow%20escape.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20because%20her%20daughter%20wanted%20them%20to%20keep%20walking%20round%20the%20market%20rather%20than%20stop%20to%20eat%20that%20they%20were%20not%20in%20the%20path%20of%20the%20car%20that%20ploughed%20through%20the%20market%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20the%20terrible%20sounds%2C%20children%20calling%20'mama%2C%20papa%2C'%2C%20'help%20me'%20-%20they're%20going%20round%20in%20my%20head%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Reis%20said%2C%20a%20tear%20trickling%20down%20her%20cheek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20young%20woman%20sobbed%2C%20bent%20double%20with%20grief%20as%20an%20older%20couple%20embraced%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20the%20attack%20drew%20comparisons%20on%20social%20media%20to%20an%20Islamist-influenced%20immigrant's%20deadly%20attack%20on%20a%20Berlin%20Christmas%20market%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%20it%20emerged%20that%20the%20suspect%2C%20a%20psychiatrist%20who%20had%20lived%20in%20Germany%20for%2018%20years%2C%20had%20criticised%20Islam%20and%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20the%20far%20right%20in%20past%20social%20media%20posts.%20This%20prompted%20damage%20control%20by%20the%20far%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMartin%20Sellner%2C%20an%20Austrian%20popular%20with%20Germany's%20far-right%2C%20posted%20on%20social%20media%20that%20the%20suspect's%20motives%20%26quot%3Bseemed%20to%20have%20been%20complex%26quot%3B%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20suspect%20%26quot%3Bhated%20Islam%2C%20but%20he%20hated%20the%20Germans%20more%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20day%20passed%2C%20politicians%2C%20including%20Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%2C%20came%20to%20lay%20flowers%20a