onflict%20with%20Wayfarer%2C%20Ms.%20Baldoni%2C%20or%20Mr.%20Heath%2C%20but%20instead%20consistently%20attempted%20to%20speak%20up%20for%20a%20safe%20and%20respectful%20workplace%20privately%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20protecting%20herself%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20cast%20and%20crew%2C%20without%20jeopardizing%20a%20film%20that%20she%20believed%20could%20make%20a%20difference%20in%20people's%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%20%26quot%3BIn%20response%2C%20Mr.%20Baldoni%2C%20Mr.%20Heath%2C%20and%20those%20working%20for%20them%2C%20sought%20to%20destroy%20Ms.%20Lively%20and%20anyone%20else%20who%20knew%20the%20truth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20a%20breakdown%20of%20the%20five%20biggest%20bombshells%20in%20Lively's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAt%20an%20'all%20hands'%20meeting%2C%20Baldoni%20and%20others%20agreed%20to%20address%20the%20'hostile%20work%20environment'%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223730%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ryan%20Reynolds%20and%20Blake%20Lively.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F676390756c531c315b892ec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222486%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBlake%20Lively's%20complaint%20said%20her%20husband%2C%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20attended%20a%20meeting%20with%20Baldoni.%3Cp%3EJamie%20McCarthy%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20says%20she%20attended%20an%20%26quot%3Ball%20hands%26quot%3B%20meeting%20with%20Baldoni%2C%20Heath%2C%20and%20others%20in%20January%20to%20discuss%20the%20%26quot%3Bhostile%20work%20environment%20that%20had%20nearly%20derailed%20production%20of%20the%20film.%26quot%3B%20Her%20husband%2C%20Ryan%20Reynolds%2C%20also%20attended%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Lively%20was%20forced%20to%20address%20concerns%20about%20Mr.%20Baldoni%20and%20Mr.%20Heath's%20misconduct%20with%20them%20directly%20and%20began%20doing%20so%20months%20before%20filming%20began%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20concerns%20she%20raised%20were%20not%20only%20for%20herself%20but%20for%20the%20other%20female%20cast%20and%20crew%2C%20some%20of%20whom%20had%20also%20spoken%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20resulted%20in%20a%20list%20of%20behaviors%20that%20Baldoni%20and%20Heath%20agreed%20to%20stop%2C%20including%20%26quot%3Bshowing%20nude%20videos%20or%20images%20of%20women%2C%20including%20the%20producer's%20wife%2C%20to%20BL%20and%2For%20her%20employees.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20behaviors%20the%20men%20agreed%20to%20cease%20were%20mentioning%20their%20%26quot%3Bprevious%20pornography%20addiction%20or%20BL's%20lack%20of%20pornography%20consumption%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bdescriptions%20of%20their%20genitalia%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreed-upon%20behaviors%20were%20compiled%20into%20a%20document%20that%20was%20shared%20with%20Wayfarer%20Studios%2C%20which%20said%20it%20found%20%26quot%3Bmost%20of%20them%20not%20only%20reasonable%20but%20also%20essential%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20all%20parties%20involved%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Cspan%3Eaccording%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBaldoni%20added%20'graphic%20content'%20to%20the%20film%20without%20Lively's%20knowledge%2C%20the%20complaint%20says%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Baldoni%20at%20the%20New%20York%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20With%20Us.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66cb4602c72ebc54a40ea1ca%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJustin%20Baldoni%20starred%20and%20directed%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20with%20Us%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ECindy%20Ord%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBaldoni%20added%20improvised%20sexual%20content%20and%20nude%20scenes%20to%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20with%20Us%26quot%3B%20in%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20unsettling%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says%2C%20including%20an%20on-camera%20orgasm%2C%20without%20Lively's%20knowledge%20or%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20Ms.%20Lively%20objected%20to%20these%20additions%2C%20Mr.%20Baldoni%20insisted%20he%20had%20added%20them%20because%20he%20was%20making%20the%20film%20'through%20the%20female%20gaze%2C'%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%20%26quot%3BAlthough%20he%20agreed%20to%20remove%20the%20scenes%2C%20he%20made%20a%20last-ditch%20attempt%20to%20keep%20one%20in%20which%20the%20couple%20orgasm%20together%20on%20their%20wedding%20night%2C%20which%20he%20said%20was%20important%20to%20him%20because%20he%20and%20his%20partner%20climax%20simultaneously%20during%20intercourse.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Baldoni%20then%20intrusively%20asked%20Ms.%20Lively%20whether%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20climax%20simultaneously%20during%20intercourse%2C%20which%20Ms.%20Lively%20found%20invasive%20and%20refused%20to%20discuss%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20also%20says%20Baldoni%20urged%20Lively%20to%20%26quot%3Bsimulate%20full%20nudity%26quot%3B%20while%20filming%20a%20scene%20in%20which%20her%20character%20gives%20birth%2C%20saying%20it's%20%26quot%3Bnot%20normal%26quot%3B%20for%20women%20to%20wear%20their%20hospital%20gowns%20while%20giving%20birth.%20Although%20Lively%20disagreed%2C%20the%20complaint%20says%20she%20compromised%20and%20agreed%20to%20be%20nude%20from%20below%20the%20chest%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENeither%20Baldoni%20nor%20Heath%20closed%20the%20set%20before%20filming%20the%20scene%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint%2C%20allowing%20%26quot%3Bnon-essential%20crew%20to%20pass%20through%20while%20Ms.%20Lively%20was%20mostly%20nude%20with%20her%20legs%20spread%20wide%20in%20stirrups%20and%20only%20a%20small%20piece%20of%20fabric%20covering%20her%20genitalia.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHeath%20also%20showed%20Lively%20and%20her%20assistant%20a%20video%20of%20his