nsumers%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-backlash-it-ends-with-us-promotion-save-reputation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecriticized%20Lively's%20marketing%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20press%20tour%2C%20which%20resulted%20in%20social%20media%20backlash%20toward%20her%20and%20her%20brands.%20Baldoni%20did%20not%20experience%20the%20same%20disapproval%20from%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20the%20public%20did%20not%20know%20was%20that%20Mr.%20Baldoni%20and%20his%20team%20did%20so%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20explain%20why%20many%20of%20the%20Film's%20cast%20and%20crew%20had%20unfollowed%20Mr.%20Baldoni%20on%20social%20media%20and%20were%20not%20appearing%20with%20him%20in%20public%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBaldoni%20and%20his%20team%20engaged%20in%20'social%20manipulation'%20to%20'destroy'%20her%20reputation%2C%20the%20complaint%20says%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Justin%20Baldoni%20did%20not%20pose%20for%20photographs%20with%20his%20castmates%20at%20the%20New%20York%20premiere%20of%20%26quot%3BIt%20Ends%20With%20Us.%26quot%3B%20He%20skipped%20the%20London%20premiere%20altogether.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66b65e7f955b01c3294d5c2a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELively%20said%20in%20her%20complaint%20that%20Baldoni%20tried%20to%20%26quot%3Bdestroy%26quot%3B%20her%20reputation.%3Cp%3EJohn%20Nacion%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%2C%20Lively%20said%20Baldoni's%20decision%20to%20switch%20marketing%20strategies%20was%20the%20start%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmulti-tiered%20plan%26quot%3B%20using%20%26quot%3Bsocial%20manipulation%26quot%3B%20to%20ultimately%20%26quot%3Bdestroy%26quot%3B%20her%20public%20reputation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaldoni%20hired%20Melissa%20Nathan%2C%20a%20crisis%20communications%20specialist%20from%20The%20Agency%20Group%20PR%2C%20on%20July%2031%20at%20the%20suggestion%20of%20his%20publicist%2C%20Jennifer%20Abel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Ms.%20Nathan%20proposed%20included%20a%20practice%20known%20as%20'Astroturfing%2C'%20which%20has%20been%20defined%20as%20'the%20practice%20of%20publishing%20opinions%20or%20comments%20on%20the%20internet%2C%20in%20the%20media%2C%20etc.%20that%20appear%20to%20come%20from%20ordinary%20members%20of%20the%20public%20but%20actually%20come%20from%20a%20particular%20company%20or%20political%20group%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20includes%20screenshots%20of%20text%20messages%20that%20Lively's%20attorneys%20say%20are%20between%20Abel%20and%20Nathan.%20In%20one%2C%20Abel%20tells%20Nathan%20that%20Baldoni%20%26quot%3Bwants%20to%20feel%20like%20she%20can%20be%20buried%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20reference%20to%20Lively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20one%2C%20Baldoni%20sent%20Abel%20a%20screenshot%20of%20a%20social%20media%20post%20about%20Hailey%20Bieber%20facing%20bullying%20allegations%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20we%20would%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20Baldoni%20wrote%20in%20the%20text%20message%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBaldoni%20and%20his%20team%20would%20%26quot%3Bfeed%20pieces%20of%20this%20manufactured%20content%20to%20unwitting%20reporters%2C%20making%20content%20go%20viral%20in%20order%20to%20influence%20public%20opinion%20and%20thereby%20cause%20an%20organic%20pile-on%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20following%20weeks%2C%20news%20outlets%20published%20numerous%20stories%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblake-lively-backlash-it-ends-with-us-promotion-save-reputation-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20%26quot%3Bbacklash%26quot%3B%20Lively%20faced%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20fans%20online%20during%20the%20film's%20press%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3