ncouraged%20them%20to%20be%20self-reliant.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20had%20to%20budget%20their%20monthly%20allowances%20and%20pick%20up%20chores%20when%20they%20wanted%20extra%20cash.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20young%20parent%2C%20Sandy%20was%20a%20self-described%20%26quot%3Byes%20mom.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20her%20two%20sons%20were%205%20or%206%2C%20Sandy%2C%20who%20uses%20a%20pseudonym%20online%20but%20has%20been%20verified%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20would%20let%20them%20do%20just%20about%20anything%20they%20asked.%20But%20they%20were%20responsible%20for%20the%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20like%20seven%20boys%20in%20the%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20they'd%20all%20come%20over%20and%20make%20cookies%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%2C%20who%20retired%20at%20age%2062%20in%20December%202019%20and%20has%20since%20built%20her%20net%20worth%20to%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%202021.%20%26quot%3BThey%20would%20make%20a%20huge%20mess%2C%20and%20it%20was%20fine%20because%20then%20I'd%20say%2C%20'OK%2C%20now%20you%20have%20to%20clean%20up%20the%20mess.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20took%20a%20similar%20approach%20to%20teaching%20her%20kids%20about%20money%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20be%20self-reliant%20and%20exposing%20them%20to%20real-world%20situations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20her%20sons%20became%20a%20millionaire%20at%20age%2035.%20He%20calls%20Sandy%20%26quot%3Bthe%20single%20biggest%20financial%20influencer%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20five%20of%20the%20most%20important%20money%20lessons%20Sandy%20taught%20her%20boys%20from%20an%20early%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236f04f25-edb4-4a1e-9e06-29dbc6aa9077%5C%22%3E1.%20How%20to%20spend%20mindfully%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESandy%20gave%20each%20of%20her%20kids%20a%20%24200%20monthly%20allowance%20starting%20around%20age%2010%20or%2011.%20At%20first%2C%20they%20were%20thrilled%2C%20she%20said%2C%20until%20they%20realized%20they%20were%20responsible%20for%20nearly%20all%20of%20their%20expenses%2C%20from%20toothpaste%20to%20hockey%20team%20dues%20(Sandy%20and%20her%20husband%20would%20cover%20essentials%20like%20food%20and%20doctor's%20visits).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20choose%20what%20you%20want%20to%20do%2C%20but%20then%20you%20don't%20have%20money%20leftover%20to%20do%20those%20other%20things.%20So%20make%20your%20choices%20wisely%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20remembered%20telling%20her%20sons.%20%26quot%3BI%20let%20them%20decide%20those%20things.%20Sometimes%20they%20made%20decisions%20I%20didn't%20think%20were%20the%20greatest%2C%20but%20that's%20how%20they%20learned.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20the%20way%2C%20Sandy%20exposed%20them%20to%20some%20of%20her%20own%20frugal%20habits%2C%20at%20one%20point%20helping%20them%20sew%20their%20own%20clothes%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d66ff31a-4249-4188-b7bb-6caa6e5c9b31%5C%22%3E2.%20How%20to%20earn%20extra%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20a%20generous%20monthly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbanking%2Fbest-debit-card-for-kids%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sandy%20allowed%20her%20sons%20to%20earn%20extra%20cash%20by%20picking%20up%20household%20chores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere'd%20always%20be%20lists%20of%20them%20on%20the%20refrigerator%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20with%20the%20pay%20listed%20next%20to%20the%20task.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20wanted%20something%20bad%20enough%2C%20they%20would%20find%20those%20jobs%20and%20do%20them%20in%20order%20to%20earn%20that%20and%20pay%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20inherited%20their%20parents'%20entrepreneurial%20spirit.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20dad%20and%20I%20had%20a%20graphic%20arts%20business%2C%20and%20we%20worked%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20the%20kids%20got%20to%20see%20how%20hard%20it%20is%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said.%20The%20boys%20would%20print%20flyers%20to%20advertise%20their%20own%20businesses%2C%20like%20raking%20a%20neighbor's%20leaves%20or%20pulling%20weeds%20in%20the%20garden%2C%20to%20keep%20the%20income%20flowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222daa7da9-1253-4a59-a65c-4fc660240d8e%5C%22%3E3.%20How%20the%20stock%20market%20works%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Christmases%20and%20birthdays%2C%20Sandy%20and%20her%20husband%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-buy-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuy%20small%20amounts%20of%20stock%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20their%20sons%20in%20companies%20they%20cared%20about%2C%20like%20the%20chocolate-maker%20Hershey's%2C%20and%20show%20them%20how%20to%20track%20the%20stock's%20performance%20in%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20just%20helps%20them%20to%20get%20interested%20in%20it%2C%20learn%20about%20it%2C%20and%20see%20how%20it%20grows%20or%20goes%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%2C%20it%20can%20go%20down%2C%20and%20you%20can%20lose%20money%2C%20but%20they%20see%20that%20when%20it's%20still%20in%20small%20pieces%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20so%20overwhelming.%26quot%3B%20They%20also%20gave%20the%20boys%20the%20choice%20of%20when%20to%20buy%20or%20sell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ec40c103-eada-481a-8f3c-192c311697d2%5C%22%3E4.%20The%20power%20of%20delayed%20gratification%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20common%20gift%20in%20Sandy's%20house%C2%A0was%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-is-a-bond%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esavings%20bonds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20bought%20bonds%20for%20the%20boys%20in%20small%20denominations%20and%20used%20them%20to%20explain%20the%20concept%20of%20delayed%20gratification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20kept%20them%20and%20waited%20for%20them%20to%20mature%20and%20cashed%20them%20in%20when%20they%20got%20older%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20interest%20rates%20were%20much%20higher%2030%20years%20ago%20than%20they%20are%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDefinitely%2C%20it%20was%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20we've%20got%20to%20wait%20all%20this%20time%20for%20this%20to%20make%20money.'%20But%20it%20showed%20them%20that's%20what%20happens%3A%20It%20compounds%2C%20and%20you%20earn%20it%20over%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc11b74f-6c71-4afc-b5fb-37c60af746d0%5C%22%3E5.%20How%20to%20be%20self-reliant%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESandy%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20her%20goal%20as%20a%20parent%20was%20to%20make%20sure%20her%20sons%20were%20financially%20independent%20by%20age%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20said%2C%20'When%20I%20die%2C%20if%20I'm%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20hospital%20in%20an%20ambulance%20and%20I%20still%20have%20a%20dime%20left%20to%20my%20name%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20have%20the%20ambulance%20pull%20over%20and%20buy%20half%20a%20candy%20bar.%20I%20am%20spending%20my%20money.%20I'm%20the%20one%20that%20earned%20it.%20I%20am%20taking%20it%2C%20I'm%20not%20leaving%20it%20to%20you%20guys.%20You%20guys%20can%20earn%20your%20own%20money.%20I%20took%20care%20of%20you%20till%20you%20were%20adults%2C'%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20entirely%20true%2C%20she%20added%2C%20but%20she%20didn't%20want%20them%20to%20think%20they%20could%20slack%20off%20and%20consider%20her%20a%20cushy%20backup%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20think%20I'm%20too%20tough%20or%20cold%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandy%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbut%20I%20just%20think%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20that%20stuff%2C%20it%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20really%20make%20kids%20realize%20how%20they%20can%20do%20it%20themselves.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDon't%20know%20where%20to%20start%3F%20Consider%20a%20financial%20advisor.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https