%20had%20had%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20information%20coming%20in%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20it%20remained%20unclear%20whether%20Tice%20was%20alive.%20%26quot%3BThe%20bottom%20line%20is%20the%20information%20that%20we%20have%20right%20now%20doesn't%20confirm%20either%20in%20one%20way%20or%20the%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-to-lift-10m-bounty-syrian-rebel-leader-jolani-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734802204000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6766dfe6e3e473ef263aad63%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-to-lift-10m-bounty-syrian-rebel-leader-jolani-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%20is%20the%20leader%20of%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%2C%20the%20rebel%20group%20that%20spearheaded%20the%20offensive%20against%20Bashar%20Assad's%20forces.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22rrommen%40insider.com%20(Rebecca%20Rommen)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-to-lift-10m-bounty-syrian-rebel-leader-jolani-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Criterion%20Collection%20Art%20Director%20Breaks%20Down%20the%20Eye-Catching%20Designs%20to%20%E2%80%98The%20Grifters%2C%20%E2%80%98The%20Piano%E2%80%99%20and%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734802200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2Fphoto-collage.png-4.png%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236256467%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Criterion%20Collection%E2%80%99s%20art%20director%20Eric%20Skillman%20is%20constantly%20collecting%20names.%20Skillman%20is%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20finding%20the%20artists%20who%20design%20or%20illustrate%20Criterion%20Collection%E2%80%99s%20DVD