parked%20sorrow%20and%20revulsion%2C%20with%20a%20nine-year-old%20child%20among%20the%20dead%20and%20casualties%20being%20treated%20in%2015%20regional%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGermany%20has%20been%20hit%20by%20multiple%20deadly%20jihadist%20attacks%2C%20but%20evidence%20gathered%20by%20investigators%20and%20his%20past%20online%20posts%20painted%20a%20different%20picture%20of%20Abdulmohsen%2C%20a%2050-year-old%20doctor%20of%20psychiatry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20self-described%20%26quot%3BSaudi%20atheist%26quot%3B%20who%20as%20an%20activist%20helped%20women%20flee%20the%20oil-rich%20kingdom%2C%20he%20has%20railed%20against%20Islam%20but%20also%20against%20what%20he%20saw%20as%20Germany's%20permissive%20attitude%20towards%20refugees%20from%20other%20mainly%20Muslim%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterior%20Minister%20Nancy%20Fraser%20said%20he%20held%20%26quot%3BIslamophobic%26quot%3B%20views%2C%20and%20a%20prosecutor%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20background%20to%20the%20crime...%20could%20have%20been%20disgruntlement%20with%20the%20way%20Saudi%20Arabian%20refugees%20are%20treated%20in%20Germany%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaha%20Al-Hajji%20of%20the%20Berlin-based%20European%20Saudi%20Organisation%20for%20Human%20Rights%20told%20AFP%20Abdulmohsen%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20psychologically%20disturbed%20person%20with%20an%20exaggerated%20sense%20of%20self-importance%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECall%20for%20unity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbdulmohsen%20in%20his%20online%20posts%20spoke%20about%20his%20troubles%20with%20and%20suspicions%20of%20German%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20August%2C%20he%20posted%20on%20social%20media%3A%20%26quot%3BIs%20there%20a%20path%20to%20justice%20in%20Germany%20without%20blowing%20up%20a%20German%20embassy%20or%20randomly%20slaughtering%20German%20citizens%3F%20...%20If%20anyone%20knows%20it%2C%20please%20let%20me%20know.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDie%20Welt%20daily%20reported%2C%20citing%20security%20sources%2C%20that%20German%20state%20and%20federal%20police%20had%20carried%20out%20a%20%26quot%3Brisk%20assessment%26quot%3B%20on%20him%20last%20year%20but%20concluded%20that%20he%20posed%20%26quot%3Bno%20specific%20danger%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20sombre%20Scholz%2C%20dressed%20in%20black%2C%20visited%20the%20attack%20site%20Saturday%20together%20with%20national%20and%20regional%20politicians%20laying%20flowers%20outside%20the%20main%20church%20in%20Magdeburg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMourning%20and%20bereaved%20residents%20have%20left%20candles%2C%20flowers%2C%20cards%20and%20children's%20toys%20at%20the%20Johanneskirche%20church%2C%20where%20a%20memorial%20service%20was%20planned%20at%207%3A00%20pm%20(1800%20GMT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScholz%20pledged%20the%20state%20would%20respond%20%26quot%3Bwith%20the%20full%20force%20of%20the%20law%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20attack%20but%20also%20called%20for%20unity%20as%20Germany%20has%20been%20rocked%20by%20a%20heated%20debate%20on%20immigration%20and%20security%20ahead%20of%20elections%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre-left%20chancellor%20said%20it%20was%20important%20%26quot%3Bthat%20we%20stick%20together%2C%20that%20we%20link%20arms%2C%20that%20it%20is%20not%20hatred%20that%20determines%20our%20coexistence%20but%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20are%20a%20community%20that%20seeks%20a%20common%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20he%20was%20grateful%20for%20expressions%20of%20%26quot%3Bsolidarity...%20from%20many%2C%20many%20countries%20around%20the%20world.%20It%20is%20good%20to%20hear%20that%20we%20as%20Germans%20are%20not%20alone%20in%20the%20face%20of%20this%20terrible%20catastrophe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Sad%20and%20shocked'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurveillance%20video%20footage%20of%20the%20attack%20showed%20a%20black%20BMW%20racing%20straight%20through%20the%20crowd%2C%20scattering%20bodies%20amid%20the%20festive%20stalls%20that%20were%20selling%20traditional%20handicrafts%2C%20snacks%20and%20mulled%20wine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20debris%20and%20discarded%20medical%20materials%20blew%20across%20the%20cordoned-off%20site%2C%20where%20stalls%20now%20stand%20empty%20around%20a%20giant%20Christmas%20tree%2C%20the%20event%20cancelled%20for%20the%20year%20out%20of%20respect%20for%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20leader%20of%20the%20far-right%20Alternative%20for%20Germany%20(AfD)%2C%20Alice%20Weidel%2C%20which%20has%20focused%20on%20jihadist%20attacks%20in%20its%20campaign%20against%20immigrants%2C%20wrote%20on%20X%3A%20%26quot%3BWhen%20will%20this%20madness%20stop%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20happened%20today%20affects%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%20It%20affects%20us%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20Fael%20Kelion%2C%20a%2027-year-old%20Cameroonian%20living%20in%20the%20city%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20since%20(the%20suspect)%20is%20a%20foreigner%2C%20the%20population%20will%20be%20unhappy%2C%20less%20welcoming.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Raarig%2C%2067%20and%20an%20engineer%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20sad%2C%20I%20am%20shocked.%20I%20never%20would%20have%20believed%20this%20could%20happen%2C%20here%20in%20an%20east%20German%20provincial%20town.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20believed%20the%20attack%20%26quot%3Bwill%20play%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20the%20AfD%26quot%3B%20which%20has%20had%20its%20strongest%20support%20in%20the%20formerly%20communist%20eastern%20Germany.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecurity%20was%20stepped%20up%20Saturday%20at%20Christmas%20markets%20elsewhere%20in%20Germany%20with%20more%20police%20seen%20in%20Hamburg%2C%20Leipzig%20and%20other%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGerman%20footballers%20were%20holding%20a%20minute's%20silence%20and%20wearing%20black%20armbands%20in%20weekend%20matches%20in%20tribute%20to%20the%20victims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regional%20Evangelical%20church%20announced%20that%20at%207%3A03%20p.m.%20(1803%20GMT)%20%26quot%3Bthe%20time%20of%20yesterday's%20attack%20on%20the%20Christmas%20market%2C%20the%20bells%20of%20all%20churches%20in%20Magdeburg%20and%20many%20places%20of%20worship%20in%20the%20surrounding%20area%20will%20ring%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734801600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Foa8ut2kg_german-christmas-market-attack_625x300_21_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-was-christmas-market-attack-suspects-possible-motive-officer-says-7302914%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chancellor%20Olaf%20Scholz%20condemned%20the%20%26quot%3Bterrible%2C%20insane%26quot%3B%20attack%20that%20killed%20five%20people%20and%20shocked%20the%20nation%2C%20days%20before%20Christmas%20and%20eight%20years%20after%20a%20jihadist%20drove%20a%20truck%20into%20a%20Christmas%20market%20in%20Berlin.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhat-was-christmas-market-attack-suspects-possible-motive-officer-says-7302914%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20avoids%20government%20shutdown%20after%20days%20of%20political%20turmoil%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734801521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F3a19%2Flive%2Ff98c8c60-bf63-11ef-a0f2-fd81ae5962f4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcqjzwq7pg0go%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Biden%20signs%20a%20budget%20to%20avert%20what%20would%20be%20the%20first%20US%20federal%20shutdown%20since%202019.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A836%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcqjzwq7pg0go%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcqjzwq7pg0go.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcqjzwq7pg0go.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ISRO%20Drafts%20Its%20First%20'POEM'%20To%20Study%20How%20Life%20Works%20In%20Space%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20for%20the%20very%20first%20time%20is%20flying%20biological%20experiments%20into%20space%20using%20a%20homegrown%20rocket.%20The%20next%20launch%20of%20the%20Polar%20Satellite%20Launch%20Vehicle%20(PSLV)%20will%20see%20not%20one%2C%20but%20three%20biological%20experiments%20with%20living%20cells%20being%20rocketed%20into%20space.%20Keeping%20living%20things%20alive%20in%20the%20hostile%20near%20vacuum%20of%20space%20is%20a%20hugely%20challenging%20task.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20fly%20living%20biological%20material%20from%20plants%20such%20as%20spinach%2C%20cowpea%2C%20and%20gut%20bacteria%20-%20three%20different%20experiments%20are%20being%20planned%20to%20be%20flown%20onboard%20the%20PSLV%20Orbital%20Experimental%20Module-4%20(POEM-4).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeeping%20any%20organism%20alive%20in%20space%20is%20a%20challenge%20as%20all%20life%20support%20systems%20have%20to%20be%20provided%20in%20a%20small%20sealed%20box.%20The%20results%20of%20the%20experiments%20also%20have%20to%20be%20gathered%20remotely.%20This%20is%20on%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20the%20PSLV%20which%20the%20Indian%20Space%20Research%20Organisation%20(ISRO)%20makes%20available%20to%20academics%20to%20conduct%20experiments%20in%20the%20real%20space%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20a%20first%20such%20venture%2C%20ISRO%20is%20flying%20live%20biological%20experiments%20into%20space%20from%20India.%20We%20would%20have%20had%20to%20start%20studies%20on%20astrobiology%20sooner%20than%20later%2C%20and%20now%20ISRO%20will%20write%20a%20whole%20new%20poem%20using%20the%20PSLV%20experimental%20platform%20and%20let%20Indian%20biologists%20explore%20all%20aspects%20of%20how%20life%20can%20survive%20in%20the%20hostile%20environment%20of%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20ISRO%20Chairman%20Dr%20S%20Somanath%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20mission%20of%20the%20PSLV%20named%20C-60%2C%20scheduled%20very%20soon%2C%20is%20actually%20a%20hugely%20experimental%20mission%20with%20the%20main%20experiment%20being%20the%20Space%20Docking%20Experiment%20(SPADEX)%20where%20ISRO%20will%20show%20for%20the%20first%20time%20docking%20and%20undocking%20of%20two%20Indian%20satellites%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F8q051iv8_isro_625x300_21_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20flask%20with%20special%20cells%20of%20the%20spinach%20plant%20that%20will%20be%20flown%20into%20space%20by%20ISRO.%20Photo%20courtesy%3A%20Amity%20University%2C%20Mumbai%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20promote%20testing%20of%20new%20ideas%20and%20technologies%2C%20ISRO%20has%20made%20the%20POEM%20platform%20available%20to%20Indian%20start-ups%20and%20its%20own%20in-house%20scientific%20teams%20to%20try%20out%20novel%20ideas.%20In%20the%20next%20mission%2C%2024%20payloads%20will%20be%20tested%20on%20the%20fourth%20stage%20of%20the%20PSLV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biological%20experiments%20being%20flown%20may%20seem%20small%20and%20elementary%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20huge%20biological%20experiments%20conducted%20onboard%20global%20space%20stations%2C%20but%20then%20at%20some%20point%20ISRO%20had%20to%20initiate%20studies%20of%20how%20life%20forms%20perform%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20small%20biological%20step%20by%20ISRO%20that%20will%20propel%20India%20closer%20to%20the%20Gaganyaan%20mission%20where%20India%20seeks%20to%20fly%20an%20Indian%20into%20space%20from%20Indian%20soil%20on%20an%20Indian%20rocket.%20More%20detailed%20experiments%20could%20also%20be%20planned%20on%20the%20Bhartiya%20Antariksha%20Station%20that%20will%20come%20up%20by%202035.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScientists%20from%20Amity%20University%2C%20Mumbai%20are%20testing%20how%20cells%20of%20common%20spinach%20perform%20in%20the%20near%20zero%20gravity%20environment%20of%20space.%20Scientists%20from%20the%20Amity%20Centre%20for%20Excellence%20in%20Astrobiology%20led%20by%20Dr%20AW%20Santhosh%20Kumar%2C%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20and%20his%20nine-member%20team%20are%20trying%20to%20decipher%20how%20a%20mass%20of%20cells%20derived%20from%20Spinacea%20oleracea%20will%20perform%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fk9nqtn48_isro_625x300_21_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20astrobiology%20team%20from%20the%20Mumbai-based%20Amity%20Centre%20for%20Excellence%20in%20Astrobiology%20led%20Dr%20AW%20Santhosh%20Kumar%2C%20Vice%20Chancellor%2C%20along%20with%20the%20small%20instrument%20seen%20in%20the%20foreground.%20Photo%20courtesy%3A%20Amity%20University%2C%20Mumbai%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERather%20than%20flying%20full%20spinach%20plants%20tissue%20culture%2C%20grown%20cells%20will%20be%20used%20as%20an%20experimental%20model.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Kumar%20said%20his%20team%20has%20designed%20a%20biological%20payload%20to%20be%20set%20on%20orbit%20through%20ISRO%20with%20an%20objective%20to%20study%20the%20possibility%20of%20food%20and%20nutrition%20during%20space%20missions.%20The%20experiment%20aims%20at%20real%20time%20monitoring%20of%20the%20biological%20payload%20in%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED