ences-moms-think-are-worth-it%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20smart%20ring%20is%20also%20%26quot%3Bconsidered%20a%20little%20premium%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20Jeffrey%20Kim%2C%20Samsung%20America's%20senior%20product%20lead%20for%20the%20Galaxy%20smart%20ring%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E2025%20is%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20the%20year%20that%20smart%20rings%20could%20go%20mainstream%20in%20a%20big%20way.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.verifiedmarketresearch.com%2Fproduct%2Fglobal-smart-ring-market-size-and-forecast%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojections%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20the%20market%20for%20smart%20rings%20taking%20off%2C%20growing%20more%20than%2020%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20until%202030.%20Over%20the%20past%20six%20months%2C%20Ultrahuman%20has%20started%20stocking%20its%20ring%20at%20major%20brick-and-mortar%20retailers%20in%20the%20US%2C%20including%20Best%20Buy%2C%20Verizon%2C%20Costco%2C%20and%20Walmart%2C%20and%20the%20company%20says%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20people%20in%20the%20US%20are%20picking%20up%20a%20new%20Ultrahuman%20ring%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f5871ae9-5e5a-4541-911b-7b918097d766%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmart%20rings%20are%20about%20more%20than%20fitness%20tracking%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20being%20used%20for%20period%20tracking%20and%20to%20predict%20illnesses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22woman%20wearing%20ring%20and%20patch%20together%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765e8595cddac6581d76ba6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUltrahuman%20also%20sells%20a%20blood%20sugar%20monitoring%20patch%20(CGM)%20that%20people%20can%20use%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20ring.%3Cp%3EUltrahuman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20studies%20have%20shown%20smart%20rings%20are%20good%20at%20picking%20up%20when%20someone%20is%20about%20to%20get%20sick%20with%20a%20viral%20illness%20like%20COVID%20or%20the%20flu%2C%20by%20combining%20metrics%20like%20heart%20rate%20variability%20with%20temperature%20and%20breathing%20rate%20while%20asleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20brands%20have%20also%20been%20carving%20out%20a%20niche%20among%20women%2C%20playing%20up%20their%20potential%20impact%20on%20women's%20health.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20women%20were%20not%20required%20to%20be%20included%20in%20medical%20research%20until%201993.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20more%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr.%20Umbereen%20Nehal%2C%20a%20fem-tech%20founder%20and%20pediatrician%2C%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20have%20accurate%2C%20personalized%20care.%20I%20would%20like%20to%20prevent%20bad%20things%20happening%20to%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWomen%20now%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20Oura%20and%20Ultrahuman%20users%20(55%25%20and%2060%25%2C%20respectively).%20Beyond%20sleep%20and%20fitness%2C%20a%20ring%20can%20use%20temperature%20to%20track%20a%20period%20%E2%80%94%20not%20a%20failsafe%20technique%2C%20but%20it's%20a%20non-invasive%20option%20to%20help%20people%20better%20plan%20when%20to%20have%20sex%20to%20conceive%20or%20avoid%20a%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENehal%20hasn't%20bought%20into%20the%20ring%20hype%20yet.%20In%20part%2C%20she%20says%20it's%20because%20the%20current%20rings%20are%20too%20%26quot%3Bugly%26quot%3B%20for%20her.%20But%20she%20also%20cautions%20consumers%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foura-smart-ring-review-why-wont-solve-back-to-work-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emaintain%20a%20%26quot%3Bhealthy%20skepticism%26quot%3B%20toward%20their%20wearables%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20not%20take%20the%20data%20insights%20or%20recommendations%20as%20health%20gospel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTry%20to%20understand%3A%20who%20was%20this%20tested%20on%3F%20Who%20was%20this%20built%20for%3F%20How%20do%20you%20want%20to%20use%20i