to%20delve%20deeper%20into%20the%20challenges%20faced%20by%20peanut%20farmers%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%2C%20while%20sitting%20at%20home%20and%20eating%20peanuts%2C%20we%20started%20talking%20about%20their%20great%20quality.%20So%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20go%20out%20and%20do%20some%20research%20to%20see%20what%20was%20happening%20on%20the%20ground%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sushant.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20major%20challenge%20faced%20by%20Unnao%E2%80%99s%20groundnut%20farmers%20was%20the%20extremely%20low%20prices%20they%20received%20for%20their%20produce.%20These%20farmers%20were%20forced%20to%20sell%20their%20groundnuts%20for%20a%20mere%20Rs%2030%20to%20Rs%2040%20per%20kilogram%2C%20without%20any%20government%20support%20or%20insurance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lack%20of%20recognition%20in%20agricultural%20surveys%20lists%20further%20exacerbated%20the%20issue.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20these%20farmers%20were%20deprived%20of%20essential%20support%20programmes%2C%20hindering%20their%20ability%20to%20earn%20a%20fair%20price%20for%20their%20hard%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAman%E2%80%99s%20research%20unveiled%20a%20potential%20solution%3A%20empowering%20farmers%20to%20undertake%20primary%20processing%20themselves.%20By%20handling%20tasks%20like%20shelling%2C%20sorting%2C%20and%20grading%2C%20farmers%20could%20significantly%20increase%20their%20earnings%20by%2050-60%25.%20To%20realise%20this%20vision%2C%20Aman%20submitted%20a%20proposal%20to%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20State%20Rural%20Livelihood%20Mission%20(UPSRLM)%20seeking%20support%20for%20establishing%20a%20producer%20group%20dedicated%20to%20primary%20processing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20Aman%E2%80%9