0could%20all%20work%20together%20for%20better%20profits.%20He%20brought%20us%20seeds%20and%20we%20worked%20on%20figuring%20out%20the%20best%20farming%20methods%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%2036-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Unnao.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%2C%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20get%20our%20soil%20tested.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20that%20was%20something%20you%E2%80%99re%20supposed%20to%20do.%20Checking%20and%20regulating%20the%20pH%20levels%2C%20nitrogen%20phosphate%2C%20and%20carbon%2016%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20any%20of%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20gain%20scientific%20perspective%2C%20Aman%20connected%20them%20with%20Dr%20Kishan%20Chandra%2C%20a%20scientist%20specialising%20in%20organic%20farming%2C%20waste%20management%2C%20and%20bio-fertiliser%20production.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20learnt%20how%20to%20make%20a%20decomposer%20solution%20%E2%80%94%20which%20is%20a%20mixture%20with%20water%20and%20essential%20nutrients%20that%20helps%20kill%20pests%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manish%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202920px)%20100vw%2C%202920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aman%20Kumar%20and%20his%20co-founder%20pose%20with%20farmers%20at%20their%20primary%20processing%20space.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515.jpeg%202920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-12-18-at-10.09.01-AM-2_11zon-1734607515-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen